<br>
Major advice.  Do not take a friend along.<br>
<br>
I took a friend along thinking I'd need help with the 3 skele's.  Before I knew it, he was dead and soon found out that Lich killed him.  What the heck is this Lich guy doing down there anyway.<br>
<br>
Anyways I got the rod and killed the 3 skele's by myself and proceeded to drag the corpse back to the entrance.  Guess what, ran into Lich Pet, got blinded, dotted, nuked, and killed.<br>
<br>
It would be best for any other Wizards in the future to go down there alone.  Those skele's will drop well enough for someone level 24 or up.<br>
<br>
